We asked questions to learn more about which businesses are already using AI, which are in the active planning phase, and which are choosing not to use AI at all. AI Adopters

AI Adopters are the 28% of respondents who report that they are already using AI in their organization. We asked them specific questions about where they are using AI, what tools they've tried, and how successful their AI adoption has been in each area. Larger businesses report higher levels of AI implementation, with Enterprises using AI at over 2x the rate of small businesses. Over the next 5 years, my company aims to integrate AI more deeply into its strategic operations. The goal would be to leverage AI to gain a competitive edge, improve innovation, and adapt to changing market demands.AI Planners

